            <scopecontent id="aspace_b44fa5f1b1c4a1e6085a4c6b2d2b807c">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Pamphlet on Baker Hospital titled <title>
                     <part>Where Sick Folks Get Well: Without Operation, Radium, or X-ray</part>
